{"id":584780,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/05/【麻辣总局】谷歌翻译瞎说什么大实话/","date":"2018-05-16T08:29:13Z","modified":"2018-05-16T08:29:13Z","title":"【麻辣总局】谷歌翻译瞎说什么大实话","content":"<p>近日，有网友发现谷歌翻译中出现了两个非常奇特（搞笑）的翻译结果，当使用日翻中（简体），分别输入“来世还在种花家”及“犯我中华者虽远必诛”时，反馈的结果分别是“来世难民”及“疯狂的中国人正处于危险之中”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/photo_2018-05-16_16-27-45.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-584781\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/photo_2018-05-16_16-27-45.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"799\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/photo_2018-05-16_16-27-45.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/photo_2018-05-16_16-27-45-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/photo_2018-05-16_16-27-45-577x1024.jpg 577w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/photo_2018-05-16_16-27-54.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-584782\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/photo_2018-05-16_16-27-54.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"799\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/photo_2018-05-16_16-27-54.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/photo_2018-05-16_16-27-54-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/photo_2018-05-16_16-27-54-577x1024.jpg 577w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>来源：爆笑祖国</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,13789],"tags":[8635,30038,34639,34637,34638]}